#PREDICADOS
#   metodo-POST
#   path-/api/users
#   header-Content-Type=application/json
#   body-substring "email".exists@example.com (contains)

#RESPOSTA
#   statuscode-409
#   Header-Content-Type=application/json
#   body- Json c error="email_exists" e msg explicativa

#TESTE- POST com JSON com "email"."exists@example.com"

POST http://localhost:2525/imposters

Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"email_duplicado",
    "port": 1515,
    "protocol":"http",
    "stubs":[
    {
            "responses":[
        {
                    "is":{
                 "statusCode":409,
                 "headers":{"Content-Type":"application/json"},
                    "body":{"error":"email_exists",
                    "msg":"O email já está registado"}
          }
        }
      ],
             "predicates":[
        {
                     "equals":{
                     "path":"/api/users",
                        "method":"POST",
                                "headers":{"Content-Type":"application/json"}
          }
        },
        {
          "contains":{
            "body":"value"
            }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

## as barras no body no contains serve para as aspas serem vistas como parte do texto

###


POST http://localhost:1515/api/users

Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "joao123",

    "email": "exists@example.com"
}


POST http://localhost:1515/api/users

Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "maria",
    "email": "maria@example.com"
}